Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底打算让我等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底在做些什么才会浪费这么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为那家伙已经离开多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:01:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整整三天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无奈得无话可说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底是有多磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那家伙还被村里的人当做眼中钉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样慢吞吞地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再遇上些什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 是要给妈妈穿的婚纱…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸是不是为了找那个花了太多时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算如此他也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的寿命也没有那么长以至于让他浪费时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你想想 爸爸说会一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是说了他愿意一直和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈你不觉得幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 时间永远不会前进的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种世界 会是什么感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:11.95,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0}act 10 空想forest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方居然有房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么近为什么至今为止都没有人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是夺走了槻彦的怪物的妖术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是槻彦说那只怪物是自己的老婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物是槻彦的老婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙肯定是被怪物的妖术操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它操纵槻彦之后 打算今后袭击村子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成那样的话事情就难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我们一起上 速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你磨磨蹭蹭什么呢 快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…感觉刚刚好像听见了脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是槻彦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我一口气痛射了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这家伙是怪物的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:29.87,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这头发…绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 把这家伙一起干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 这家伙不是还小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在磨磨蹭蹭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 我亲自来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目隐」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么 她居然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…是妖术？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目觉」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先…先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目欺」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目夺」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目合」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲起来也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你们逃到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能立刻知道你们的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槻彦他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你执意不说的话那我就直接读取你的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目盗」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快点把操纵你的怪物的所在之处告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是不想揍你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们不能放着来历不明的东西不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓟…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓟是我的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要对她…出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 为什么你要包庇那只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还要反抗的话 我可不会手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在包庇她 我不是全都告诉你们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的家人永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有一些类似标记的东西好像一直延续到森林方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 槻彦这家伙为了回去好像做好了准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上做好降服怪物的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也该醒醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能降服了那家伙你也能醒过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快点做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底对我做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后不要再带任何人到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了的话 就快点给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槻彦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再因为我而伤害你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视天道 甚至将你们无端卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实早就已经发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为有我存在所以才会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就可以如我所愿幸福地生活在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我不奢求幸福的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想做个美梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个能与家人永远生活在一起的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很爱你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们的爱无以复加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 你不是什么怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要使用这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我可能没有资格说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你要作为一个人类和你父亲幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是 我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要走 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都爱着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都会祈祷 你们能够幸福地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说过不行啊 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又想一个人偷偷跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…外面看上去很好玩的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 不要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈念故事给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 当然可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来这边和妈妈一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就讲这个故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从妈妈消失留下我们的那天直到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底过了多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管父亲去世的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是茉莉出生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈都没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她是否依旧一个人在那个无法终究的世界里独自生活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人等待着也许某天就会回来的妈妈就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等茉莉再长大一些 就让她看看外面的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界一定会接纳这个孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像妈妈对我说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在茉莉的幸福就是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不知道什么时候睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你在的话就快点回应我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怪物好像不止一只啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么久远的故事到现在还有什么可信度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 拜其所赐我们也找到了些有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看她的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果做成展品给人看的话 可是能大赚一笔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 快点放开那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你个怪物在那里说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吵 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要不要把她也抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你听我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…没能…获得幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到是你故意把她们拉进来 你也不是什么好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个永远无法完结的世界的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是最为了解的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我怎么能闭嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺从一己之利寻求安逸的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而创造了这个世界的人不就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来你的愿望原本就是带着挚爱的家人来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这样不就非常好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母女还有孙女三人能够相见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愿望终于实现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你是多么愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 没错 就是要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那利己主义 和其他相比才能带给我们最高的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑 一切…都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这表情真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招致这一切悲剧的原因就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少…也要让这个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自己主动放弃了女王蛇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它能够成功寄宿的话 应该会变成那孩子的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样 能够抑制这个世界的人就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿于你体内的蛇因为女王的消失又会如何狂躁不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不会让你留下寂寞的回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这个世界内所下达的「吞噬8月15日逝去的生命」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一指示再也无人能够阻止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 我就不应该离家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是修哉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为修哉总是对人家恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又自动地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你和家人走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…可能也和你一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那双红红的眼睛也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 再也不能走散了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救…我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了我的眼睛就会变成石头的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成石头…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 我必须要一个人待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你快点回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「救救我」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤我的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我也和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也总是非常害怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害怕也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 那个孩子去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢下我一个人就跑去别的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我好渴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不烫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在那种地方睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是忘事先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘事先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也经常忘记一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:20:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想如果我能记住很多事情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只记得一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…想要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要…和朋友一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我只记得这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…只想和朋友一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你就和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢和我做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能介绍我的朋友给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肯定也很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经是深夜零点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是请看这拥堵的人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直难以置信 到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如观众所见 现场变得很混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 我听得见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定都在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女失去了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常 非常重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女一个人哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想再和大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女反覆如此祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎有什么对少女说道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让你的愿望实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让你的期望成真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给予你一个能实现你的空想的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(203,231.5)\bord0\fs27\shad2}act11:赏月recital
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受…受够了 这种世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的内心 生命 理想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在愿望面前都是无价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入歌
